{"tid":2275684,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"連登已經痴線到5P字都唔屌得","createTime":"2020-11-07T10:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-08T02:24:19.000Z","uid":106001,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"3ea77882f517a24df968f8946a5a8039f3956253","tid":2275684,"uid":106001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:35:17.000Z","msg":"明明識個正字點解要用別字?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n&quot;唔係咁呀&quot;就唔係香港文化?<br />\n定係呢幾個字好難打唔識打?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n由細到大無論msn定online game都係打正字<br />\n身邊啲fd 10個有9個都係打正字<br />\n我都明呢1/2年多咗好多新會然<br />\n有時認真po有5P字都唔會理,專注睇內文<br />\n但依加乜鳩po都5P字仲要惡到屌返人轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申本身唔會突登捉人用5P字<br />\n但成日見到有巴打屌鳩人用5P字反而俾人負皮/屌返轉頭真係睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df8e015f8838dcd05b1c646a55052a32343c4cb7","tid":2275684,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":36,"score":-34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:38:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2391248ad65b3c253267f14a1b3f963fee4e5176","tid":2275684,"uid":205442,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:39:01.000Z","msg":"好掛住肥絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b005fa3ee384f9caa1dfd540c342821bfce83a33","tid":2275684,"uid":106001,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"df8e015f8838dcd05b1c646a55052a32343c4cb7","tid":2275684,"uid":49336,"like":2,"dislike":36,"score":-34,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:38:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-07T10:39:13.000Z","msg":"咪話吾睇唔過眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b70a2a18ccdc1732afde8ef8474e12836306a94","tid":2275684,"uid":160263,"like":0,